description: Esrey Resources Ltd. engages in the recovery of zinc, lead, and other metal by-products from primary and secondary waste materials. The company was formerly known as Esrey Energy Ltd. and changed its name to Esrey Resources Ltd. in October 2017. Esrey Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Allen Dwight Leschert B.Com., LLB
